                                    NOTE:

 After "Nocturnal Flowers" & "Nightshift" here comes the third Solee 'Best Of' album with a collection of all his current originals and remixes. Including his hit-singles "Zebra", "Caillou", "Sommerliebe" and his remixes of Wankelmut's "My Head is a Jungle" and AKA AKA's summerhit "Springtide"! A real must-have for all melodic house & techno lovers!
